      <title>调查显示莫迪的预算将推动印度股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/modi-s-budget-to-send-india-s-soaring-stocks-higher-survey-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场观察人士表示，受政府支出和企业盈利持续增长的推动，规模达 5 万亿美元的印度股市全年有望上涨 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/modi-s-budget-to-send-india-s-soaring-stocks-higher-survey-says</guid>
