      <title>特朗普保持低调，拜登因竞选面临愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trump-stays-out-of-fray-as-democrats-question-biden-s-candidacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普终于学会了政治的一条重要规则：当你的敌人犯错时，永远不要打断他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trump-stays-out-of-fray-as-democrats-question-biden-s-candidacy</guid>
